OL,3,CWoman's dream retirement ruined as
OL,4,Cmesh surgery leaves her in constant
OL,5,Cpain
OL,7,FA woman says she has had to cancel her
OL,8,Fretirement plans due to being left in
OL,9,Fconstant pain after having mesh
OL,10,Fsurgery.
OL,12,FConsultant Antony Dixon has been
OL,13,Fsuspended from practicing medicine for
OL,14,Fsix months after being found guilty of
OL,15,Fmisconduct by a medical tribunal.
OL,17,FHe pioneered a type of mesh surgery
OL,18,Fbut has since been found to have
OL,19,Fharmed patients.
