OL,3,CWoman's dream retirement ruined as
OL,4,Cmesh surgery leaves her in constant
OL,5,Cpain
OL,7,FShe said the retirement plans she had
OL,8,Fwith her husband have "gone out the
OL,9,Fwindow", adding: "We have to plan
OL,10,Feverything - I can't leave the house
OL,11,Fwithout knowing there's a toilet
OL,12,Fwithin 15 minutes. If we go anywhere,
OL,13,Fmy husband has to look up where all
OL,14,Fthe toilets are.
OL,16,F"We always said that once we'd retired
OL,17,Fwe'd spend the money travelling the
OL,18,Fworld and go and see relatives in
OL,19,FAustralia and things like that... but
OL,20,Fno."
