OL,7,FShe said she also avoids staying at
OL,8,Fother people's houses and is unable to
OL,9,Feat the food that she loves the most.
OL,11,FJosie also believes her surgery was
OL,12,Fnot needed.
OL,14,F"I can honestly say that every
OL,15,Foperation was very quick," she said.
OL,16,F"There was never an alternative
OL,17,Foffered.
