OL,5,Cpain
OL,7,F"I believe it's true that if he'd have
OL,8,Fdone one of the diagnostic tests
OL,9,Fbefore the LVMR I would never have had
OL,10,Fit because it clearly showed it was my
OL,11,Fbowel - not my pelvic floor."
OL,13,FJosie is one of 200 patients who
OL,14,Freceived an apology from North Bristol
OL,15,FNHS Trust over unnecessary operations.
OL,17,FThe Spire Hospital, North Bristol NHS
OL,18,FTrust and Anthony Dixon declined to
OL,19,Fcomment on individual cases.
