OL,7,FIn response to the Medical
OL,8,FPractitioners Tribunal findings
OL,9,Fagainst him, Mr Dixon has apologised
OL,10,Fto his patients.
OL,12,FHe said: "I have accepted the findings
OL,13,Fof misconduct made against me by the
OL,14,FMedical Practitioners Tribunal.
OL,16,F"Despite my wrongdoing, my only wish
OL,17,Fwas to make (my patients) better. I
OL,18,Fconsidered that I was acting in my
OL,19,Fpatients' best interests, as the
OL,20,Ftribunal have accepted.
OL,26,@yD@MpmyD@Ypn
